ng love.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aFrench fictiony20th century. 0aMan-woman relationshipsvFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aPolizzotti, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z97831106725030 cprintz978030021589240uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021891640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300218916423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300218916/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY